    "chemicalDescription": [
      "Dimethicone/Phenyl Silsesquioxane/Phenyl Bis-Silsesquioxane Crosspolymer is a silicone resin formed by hydrolyzing and condensing a mixture of phenyl triethoxysilane, dimethyl dimethoxysilane, and bis(trimethoxysilylethyl)benzene in a suitable solvent. The resin is then surface-treated with trimethylchlorosilane or heaxamethyldisilazane."
